Venues.Message:
1. As per the State Government Guidelines , In order to enter the cinema, it`s mandatory to have a Covid 19 vaccine (One dose at least) for guest above 18+. Vaccination certificate will be verified at the cinema entry, no entry will be permitted for non-vaccinated guest and tickets will not be refunded.
2. For your own safety, wearing face masks is compulsory for entering the cinema premises.
3. If a guest consumes alcohol or drugs will not be allowed inside the cinema and tickets are not refundable.
4. Children above the age of 3 years require tickets for U or U/A rated movies.
5. Smoking and drinking alcohol and chewing of pan are strictly prohibited. Intoxicated persons (as determined by our staff) will not be admitted.
6. Outside food and beverages are not allowed.
7. Guests aged fewer than 18 will not be allowed in A rated movies.
8. Tickets once purchased cannot be cancelled, exchanged or refunded.
9. Decision(s) taken by Miraj, shall be final and binding, rights of admission reserved.
10. 3D glass usage fee is non refundable.
11. We regret the inconvenience caused by security checks. We request your full cooperation.
12. The management will not be responsible for the loss or damage of any personal property.
13. For more info & TnC of ``CELEBRATION COMBO OFFER``please refer to the offer page.
